[pybind11] Add synonym(s) that are forward-compatible with nanobind

These help ease Drake's transition to nanobind.
See https://github.com/RobotLocomotion/drake/issues/21572.

--- include/pybind11/pybind11.h
+++ include/pybind11/pybind11.h
@@ -1281,6 +1281,9 @@
         }
         return reinterpret_steal<module_>(obj);
     }
+    static module_ import_(const char *name) {
+        return module_::import(name);
+    }
 
